Efendimiz'in konumu nazarı itibara alınırsa, fasvir inne vadallahi hakkun.

62
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:19,080
Allah sana elif laa min gulibetevum feednel ard ve hum min ba'di

63
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:23,400
galebihim seyalibun demiş de, fasvir inne vadallahi hakkun.

64
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:28,740
Laqad sadaqallahu rasula r-ruyya bilhaqq la tadkhuluna almasjida alharamun.

65
